<section class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About me</h2>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
                I really love doing sports. I have tried many: 🤸🏼, ⚽, 🏃🏼‍♂️, 🏋🏼‍♂️, 🏊🏻‍♂️, 🏇🏼... and doing them, especially with other people, is probably one of the things that makes me most fulfilled and happy. In <a href="/blog/sports">this</a> blog post I talk more in depth about this concept.
      </p>
      <p>
        Right now, I’m training for the 100 meter sprint, but I still go to the gym to easily smash my brother at everything that involves upper body strength.
      </p>
      <p>
        Other things that I love are escape rooms, chess and everything that allows me to use my brain intensively.
      </p>
      <p>
        During my free time, I pretend to be a software engineer 🤡. The projects I enjoy most are the ones that demand intense logical thinking and heavily rely on complex algorithms or data structures.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
